Feature: Navigate from Home Page
As a user
So that I can use BUDeals website
I want to buy or sell products

Scenario: Register
Given I am on http://localhost:3000
Then I press "Register"
Then I am on http://localhost:3000/students/new
Then show me the registration page

Scenario: Login
Given I am on http://localhost:3000
Then I press "Login"
Then I am on http://localhost:3000/static_pages/login
Then show me the login page

Scenario: FAQs
Given I am on http://localhost:3000
Then I press "FAQ"
Then I am on http://localhost:3000/static_pages/faq
Then show me the FAQ page
